{"tid":2111434,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓團BLACKPINK成員　Rosé姐姐美貌首度曝光！","createTime":"2020-07-16T14:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T12:09:49.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"37c083da1bdc444f6466b2dbe0475282de85c89e","tid":2111434,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:00:41.000Z","msg":"韓國女團BlACKPINK四位成員在全球享高知名度，日前與女神卡卡合作後，更讓她們知名度水漲船高，除了洋娃娃泰籍成員Lisa外，現年23歲的Ros&eacute;（朴彩英）憑藉出色的歌唱技巧和優質甜美的外表，同樣俘虜不少粉絲。日前成員Ros&eacute;於社群平台IG上，貼出她與親姐姐的合照，瞬間成為熱議話題。<br />\n<br />\nRos&eacute;於紐西蘭奧克蘭出生，7歲移民澳洲並在墨爾本長大，在網上一直流傳她有一個姐姐Alice朴智英（音譯），傳聞中Alice有著高學歷，更有著與Ros&eacute;同樣地出眾外表。連帶她的家人也得到關注。<br />\n<br />\n日前，Ros&eacute;親姐姐外表終於首度曝光，Ros&eacute;罕見於IG限時動態中，曬出她為姐姐慶生合照，並寫道：「祝這個世界上我最愛的人生日快樂。」只見到Alice留著一頭秀髮外表清秀，看上去還和Ros&eacute;有幾分相似，都擁有清秀姣好的外貌。<br />\n<br />\n據瞭解，1993年出生Alice今年27歲，畢業於澳洲國立大學法律系，現在則是一名律師。Alice美貌在粉絲圈中很有名。Ros&eacute;曾在SNS中上傳一張花籃的照片，祝賀姐姐通過律師考試，足見姊妹的感情非常要好，而粉絲們也讚嘆Ros&eacute;家姐「神級美貌」絕對才貌雙全。"},{"pid":"d5cd614a57788ed1027ca9ebab2c65ee56d9bfbd","tid":2111434,"uid":16659,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/16/2667403-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F16%2F2667403-XXL.jpg&h=736d6e75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Ros&eacute;先前貼出她與親姐姐（左）合照。（圖／翻攝自roses_are_rosie IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/16/2667413-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F16%2F2667413-XXL.jpg&h=aefbb7f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Ros&eacute;的親姐姐Alice為律師。（圖／翻攝自baebaealice IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/16/2667418-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F16%2F2667418-XXL.jpg&h=df6913fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Alice與Ros&eacute;一樣擁有「神級美貌」。（圖／翻攝自baebaealice IG）"},{"pid":"8a9c9fb1aef051f390cc09ea5e78be2d3daee8bc","tid":2111434,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"彩英系唔出辣殺!"},{"pid":"877575677cbb2c555cafeeb402e9e86af1c09a8d","tid":2111434,"uid":152432,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"屌打另一個彩英"},{"pid":"045adb030c681ddf8fc0aa8b1077f54d347f5c80","tid":2111434,"uid":15371,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"姐妹丼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484b33f9b8839ddaee2daef31367c192194d046b","tid":2111434,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":27,"score":-26,"quote":{"pid":"877575677cbb2c555cafeeb402e9e86af1c09a8d","tid":2111434,"uid":152432,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"屌打另一個彩英"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aDM4KwV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaDM4KwV.gif&h=c89ddd28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vRW2bO3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvRW2bO3.gif&h=6f301952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XdQijyi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXdQijyi.gif&h=f0ebefda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>我頭寒啦</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e0eb0e46f837482df2e95927bc04b8438fa293f0","tid":2111434,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"好想奶rose對淫腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c7295dbd0d0994482d4e803e65664bcb19d09b","tid":2111434,"uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"045adb030c681ddf8fc0aa8b1077f54d347f5c80","tid":2111434,"uid":15371,"like":4,"d